" Commands {{{1

" Enable soft wrap with ':Wrap'
command! -nargs=* Wrap setlocal wrap linebreak nolist

" Quick spell lang switch
command! En set spelllang=en
command! Fr set spelllang=fr

" Key maps {{{1

" Allow backspace in insert mode
